---
title: Teriyaki Chicken & Veggie Stir-Fry with Basmati Rice
description: It’s a teriyaki chicken stir-fry, do we need to say anything more? If we do, then the sauce will have your mouth watering in seconds and the veggies will be scrumptious and nutritious, there’s even pops of ginger in there to really make it perfect.

*We’ve replaced the Asian stir-fry mix in this recipe with broccoli florets due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
